q_comment: I find the task very useful, I could imagine using this frequently if it were released to the public.
I think this tool would be very useful and hope it can go across multiple platforms.
was honestly shocked spirited away was listed
Very interesting and useful platform, I'd enjoy using this to search and watch movies.

The interface felt very clunky and it was hard to scroll.
I would have liked being able to individually rank movies.  Or perhaps be able to add or delete some movies from a row.  Then I think the system would get an even better idea of what movies I prefer.

The groupings should make sense and many times they didn't
Too many recommendations at a time was a bit overwhelming.
